Verify that receiving a new representation of a resource
removes old representations from the cache.

-- cache.txt --
GET http://www.example.com/foo HTTP/1.1
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:00:00 GMT

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: 15
Cache-Control: max-age=59
ETag: "xyzzy"
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:00:00 GMT

Hello, World!
GET http://www.example.com/foo HTTP/1.1
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:01:00 GMT

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: 23
Cache-Control: max-age=59
ETag: "new"
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:01:00 GMT

this is the new stuff
GET http://www.example.com/foo HTTP/1.1
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:02:00 GMT

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: 23
Cache-Control: max-age=59
ETag: "new"
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:02:00 GMT

this is the new stuff
-- server.txt --
GET http://www.example.com/foo HTTP/1.1
Host: www.example.com
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:00:00 GMT

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: 15
Cache-Control: max-age=59
ETag: "xyzzy"
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:00:00 GMT

Hello, World!
GET http://www.example.com/foo HTTP/1.1
Host: www.example.com
If-None-Match: "xyzzy"
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:01:00 GMT

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: 23
Cache-Control: max-age=59
ETag: "new"
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:01:00 GMT

this is the new stuff
GET http://www.example.com/foo HTTP/1.1
Host: www.example.com
If-None-Match: "new"
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:02:00 GMT

HTTP/1.1 304 Not Modified
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: 23
Cache-Control: max-age=59
ETag: "new"
Date: Sat, 01 Jan 2000 00:02:00 GMT

